msgstr "Iz izbora izključi vozle"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mirror / Rotate makes copies"
msgstr "Zrcali / Zavrti naredi kopije"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set, the mirror and rotate functions will make a copy of the selection, "
"otherwise the selected area is moved"
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljeno, bosta funkciji zrcaljenja in vrtenja naredili kopijo "
"izbora, sicer se izbrano območje premakne"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Mirror Selection</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Horizontally</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>Izbira zrcala</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vodoravno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mirror the selected area horizontally, &ie; flipped from left to right"
msgstr ""
"Vodoravno zrcaljenje izbranega območja, &ie; obrnjen z leve proti desni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Mirror Selection</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vertically</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>Izbira zrcaljenja</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Navpično</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mirrors the selected area vertically, &ie; flipped from top to bottom"
msgstr "Zrcali izbrano območje navpično, &ie;. obrnjena od zgoraj navzdol"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Rotate Selection</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>90 degrees</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>Zavrti izbor</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>90 stopinj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the selected area anti clockwise 90 degrees"
msgstr "Zavrti izbrano območje za 90 stopinj v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Rotate Selection</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>180 degrees</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>Zavrti izbor</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>180 stopinj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the selected area anti clockwise 180 degrees"
msgstr ""
"Zavrti izbrano območje v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca za 180 stopinj"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: commands.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Rotate Selection</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>270 degrees</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>Zavrti izbor</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>270 stopinj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the selected area anti clockwise 270 degrees"
msgstr ""
"Zavrti izbrano območje v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca za 270 stopinj"

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cut, Copy and Paste"
msgstr "Izreži, kopiraj in prilepi"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cutting and copying areas of the pattern can make use of stitch and color "
"masks and the exclusion of backstitches and knots to limit the selection."
msgstr ""
"Območja rezanja in kopiranja vzorca lahko uporabijo šive in barvne maske ter "
"izključitev hrbtnih šivov in vozlov za omejitev izbire."

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The paste operation in &kxstitch; allows you to press and hold the &LMB; "
"down roughly in the position that the paste data is to go which will provide "
"an image of the paste data to allow accurate positioning before releasing "
"the mouse button to finalize the position. This technique is also used for "
"the mirroring and rotate functions. The cursor keys can also be used to move "
"the pasted pattern around and the &Enter; key used to fix the position."
msgstr ""
"Operacija lepljenja v &kxstitch; vam omogoča, da pritisnete in držite &LMB; "
"navzdol približno v položaju, kamor naj gredo prilepljeni podatki, kar bo "
"zagotovilo sliko prilepljenih podatkov, da se omogoči natančno "
"pozicioniranje, preden spustite gumb miške, da dokončate položaj. Ta tehnika "
"se uporablja tudi za funkcije zrcaljenja in vrtenja. S smernimi tipkami "
"lahko premikate tudi prilepljeni vzorec in tipko &Enter; tipka, ki se "
"uporablja za fiksiranje položaja."

