msgid "Small Full Stitch"
msgstr "Majhen polni šiv"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A small full stitch, the position is determined by the quadrant of the cell "
"selected"
msgstr "Majhen polni šiv, položaj je določen s kvadrantom izbrane celice"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "French Knot"
msgstr "Francoski vozel"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "French Knot Stitch"
msgstr "Šiv francoski vozel"

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paint"
msgstr "Naslikaj"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Paint stitches onto the canvas - Press down the &LMB; and drag around the "
"window. Stitches will be added to each cell passed over. Release the mouse "
"button to stop painting."
msgstr ""
"Naslikaj šive na platnu - Pritisnite &LMB; in povlecite po oknu. Šivi bodo "
"dodani čez vsako celico. Spustite gumb miške, da ustavite slikanje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw"
msgstr "Nariši"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw a line of stitches onto the canvas - Press down the &LMB; at the start "
"of the line, drag to the required end point of the line and release the "
"mouse button. Stitches will be added to each cell that the line passes "
"through."
msgstr ""
"Nariši linijo šivov na platno - pritisnite &LMB; na začetku črte povlecite "
"do želene končne točke črte in spustite tipko miške. Šivi bodo dodani vsaki "
"celici, skozi katero gre črta."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Erase"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Erase stitches - Press down the &LMB; and drag over the stitches to be "
"deleted. All stitches within the cells passed over will be removed. Release "
"the mouse button to stop erasing. To erase backstitches hold down the &Ctrl; "
"key and left click in the start or end point of the backstitch, if there is "
"more than one backstitch at the digitized point this method will erase the "
"first one found. To delete a specific backstitch, click and drag from one "
"end to the other. To erase french knots hold down the &Shift; key and left "
"click on the knot to delete it."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje šivov - Pritisnite &LMB; in povlecite čez šive, ki jih želite "
"izbrisati. Odstranjeni bodo vsi šivi v celicah, ki so bile prevlečene. "
"Spustite tipko miške, da ustavite brisanje. Če želite izbrisati povratne "
"šive, držite &Ctrl; tipko in levi klik na začetni ali končni točki hrbtnega "
"šiva; če je na digitalizirani točki več kot en zadnji šiv, bo ta metoda "
"izbrisala prvega najdenega. Če želite izbrisati določen zadnji šiv, kliknite "
"in povlecite od enega konca do drugega. Če želite izbrisati francoske vozle, "
"držite &Shift; tipko in levi klik na vozel, da ga izbrišete."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw Rectangle"
msgstr "Nariši pravokotnik"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw a rectangle - Press down the &LMB; at one corner of the rectangle and "
"drag to the opposite corner. Release the mouse button and an unfilled "
"rectangle of stitches will be added to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Nariše pravokotnik - pritisnite &LMB; v enem kotu pravokotnika in povlecite "
"v nasprotni kot. Spustite tipko miške in na platno bo dodan nezapolnjen "
"pravokotnik šivov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fill Rectangle"
msgstr "Izpolni pravokotnik"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw a filled rectangle - Press down the &LMB; at one corner of the "
"rectangle and drag to the opposite corner. Release the mouse button and a "
"filled rectangle of stitches will be added to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Nariše zapolnjen pravokotnik - pritisnite &LMB; v enem kotu pravokotnika in "
"povlecite v nasprotni kot. Spustite tipko miške in na platno bo dodan "
"zapolnjen pravokotnik šivov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw Ellipse"
msgstr "Nariši elipso"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw an ellipse - Press down the &LMB; at one corner of the ellipse and drag "
"to the opposite corner. Release the mouse button and an unfilled ellipse of "
"stitches will be added to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Nariše elipso - Pritisnite &LMB; v enem kotu elipse in povlecite v nasprotni "
"kot. Spustite tipko miške in na platno bo dodana nezapolnjena elipsa šivov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fill Ellipse"
msgstr "Izpolni elipso"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw a filled ellipse - Press down the &LMB; at one corner of the ellipse "
"and drag to the opposite corner. Release the mouse button and a filled "
"ellipse of stitches will be added to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Nariše zapolnjeno elipso - pritisnite &LMB; v enem kotu elipse in povlecite "
"v nasprotni kot. Spustite tipko miške in na platno bo dodana zapolnjena "
"elipsa šivov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fill Polygon"
msgstr "Izpolni poligon"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw a filled polygon - Click on each cell marking the vertexes of the "
"polygon, click and drag to create more complex curves. Each of the vertexes "
"are marked by a circle with a black line joining them. To close the polygon "
"click on the starting cell again. You can use the &Backspace; key to remove "
"the last point, or the &Esc; key to remove all vertexes and cancel the "
"operation."
msgstr ""
"Nariše zapolnjen mnogokotnik – Kliknite vsako celico, ki označuje oglišča "
"mnogokotnika, kliknite in povlecite, da ustvarite bolj zapletene krivulje. "
"Vsako oglišče je označeno s krogom s črno črto, ki ju povezuje. Za zapiranje "
"poligona znova kliknite začetno celico. Uporabite lahko &Backspace; tipko za "
"odstranitev zadnje točke ali &Esc; tipko za odstranitev vseh vozlišč in "
"preklic operacije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Besedilo"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert text in stitches. This invokes the text dialog. Select the font "
"required and the size, enter the text and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. "
"Press the &LMB; roughly where you would like the text, move the mouse to "
"position the text accurately and then release the mouse button. This is the "
"same as the paste function."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi besedilo v šive. To prikliče besedilno pogovorno okno. Izberite "
"želeno pisavo in velikost, vnesite besedilo in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>. Pritisnite &LMB; približno tja, kamor želite besedilo, "
"premaknite miško, da natančno postavite besedilo, in nato spustite gumb "
"miške. To je enako kot funkcija lepljenja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alphabet"
msgstr "Alphabet"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert patterns from the currently selected library that match the keys "
"pressed. This allows the creation of pattern alphabets that can have a key "
"assignment. After selecting this tool and clicking a position on the pattern "
"for the insertion point, each key pressed will be searched for in the "
"current library for a matching pattern. If found this will be inserted at "
"the position on the pattern and the insertion position then advanced by the "
"width of the inserted character pattern. The pattern space will be extended "
"right to allow further characters to be entered. Pressing &Enter; will start "
"a new line under the position of the original insertion point, the pattern "
"space will be extended downwards to accommodate the new line if insufficient "
"space is available. &Backspace; will delete the last character entered and "
"the <keycap>Space</keycap> key will advance the insertion point by either "
"the width of a space character in the library or a predetermined amount if "
"no space character exists. The text will wrap onto the next line if the edge "
"of the pattern is reached and the end of a word is detected."
msgstr ""
"Vstavite vzorce iz trenutno izbrane knjižnice, ki se ujemajo s pritisnjenimi "
"tipkami. To omogoča ustvarjanje vzorčnih abeced, ki imajo lahko dodelitev "
"ključa. Ko izberete to orodje in kliknete položaj na vzorcu za točko "
"vstavljanja, bo vsaka pritisnjena tipka v trenutni knjižnici poiskana za "
"ujemajoči se vzorec. Če ga najdemo, bo ta vstavljen na mesto vzorca in "
"položaj vstavljanja se bo nato pomaknil za širino vstavljenega vzorca "
"znakov. Prostor za vzorec bo razširjen desno, da bo omogočen vnos nadaljnjih "
"znakov. S pritiskom &Enter; bo začel novo vrstico pod položajem prvotne "
"točke vstavljanja, bo prostor vzorca podaljšan navzdol, da se prilagodi novi "
"vrstici, če ni na voljo dovolj prostora. &Backspace; bo izbrisal zadnji "
"vneseni znak in tipka <keycap>Presledek</keycap> bo premaknila točko "
"vstavljanja za širino presledka v knjižnici ali vnaprej določeno količino, "
"če presledek ne obstaja. Če je dosežen rob vzorca in je zaznan konec besede, "
"se besedilo prelije v naslednjo vrstico."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select"
msgstr "Izberi"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a rectangular region - Press down the &LMB; at one corner of the "
"rectangle, drag to the opposite corner and release the button. A selection "
"rectangle is shown to indicate the area."
msgstr ""
"Izbere pravokotno območje - Pritisnite &LMB; v enem kotu pravokotnika "
"povlecite v nasprotni kot in spustite gumb. Prikazan je izbirni pravokotnik, "
"ki označuje območje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color picker"
msgstr "Izbirnik barv"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows the selection of a color from the existing stitches. Hovering over "
"stitches will show a tool tip indicating the color under the cursor. "
"Clicking with the &LMB; will select it."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro barve med obstoječimi šivi. Če miškin kazalec premaknete nad "
"šive, se prikaže nasvet orodja, ki označuje barvo pod kazalcem. S klikom z "
"&LMB; ga bo izbral."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backstitch"
msgstr "Hrbtni šiv"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add backstitching to the canvas - Press down the &LMB; at the start of the "
"backstitch, it will snap to the closest of 9 points in the cell, drag to the "
"end point of the backstitch and release the mouse button, again this will "
"snap to the nearest of 9 points in the cell."
msgstr ""
"Dodaj hrbtno šivanje na platno – Pritisnite &LMB; na začetku hrbtnega šiva "
"se bo zaskočil na najbližjo od 9 točk v celici, povlecite do končne točke "
"hrbtnega šiva in spustite gumb miške, to se bo znova zaskočilo na najbližjo "
"od 9 točk v celici."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Palette Menu"
msgstr "Meni palete"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Palette Manager"
msgstr "Upravljalnik palet"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add and remove colors to the current palette. Assign symbols and the number "
"of strands for the stitching and backstitching."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte in odstranite barve v trenutno paleto. Določite simbole in število "
"pramenov za šivanje in hrbtno šivanje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Symbols"
msgstr "Prikaži simbole"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the symbols associated with each color"
msgstr "Pokažite simbole, povezane s posamezno barvo"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear Unused"
msgstr "Počisti Neuporabljeno"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the unused colors from the palette."
msgstr "Odstrani neuporabljene barve iz palete."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Swap Colors"
msgstr "Premenjaj barve"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next color selected will be swapped with the currently selected color. "
"If you select the eye dropper tool, you can choose the color to be swapped "
"with directly from the pattern."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja izbrana barva bo zamenjana s trenutno izbrano barvo. Če izberete "
"orodje za kapalko, lahko izberete barvo, ki jo želite zamenjati, neposredno "
"iz vzorca."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace Colors"
msgstr "Zamenjaj barve"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next color selected will replace the currently selected color. As with "
"swap colors, you can use the eye dropper tool to select the color from the "
"pattern."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja izbrana barva bo nadomestila trenutno izbrano barvo. Tako kot pri "
"zamenjavi barv lahko uporabite orodje kapalke, da izberete barvo iz vzorca."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Library Menu"
msgstr "Meni knjižnice"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "Library Manager"
msgstr "Upravljalnik knjižnice"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the pattern library manager which is a non modal dialog allowing the "
"creation and use of libraries of patterns or alphabets. Drag and drop is "
"available to allow the dragging and dropping of patterns from the library to "
"the pattern. Automatic conversion of flosses to suit the current pattern and "
"scaling of the image to the current pattern scale for accurate positioning."
msgstr ""
"Odprite upravitelja knjižnice vzorcev, ki je nemodalno pogovorno okno, ki "
"omogoča ustvarjanje in uporabo knjižnic vzorcev ali abeced. Na voljo je "
"možnost povleci in spusti, ki omogoča vlečenje in spuščanje vzorcev iz "
"knjižnice v vzorec. Samodejna pretvorba nitk, da ustrezajo trenutnemu "
"vzorcu, in prilagajanje lestvice slike na trenutno lestvico vzorca za "
"natančno pozicioniranje."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Pattern Menu"
msgstr "Meni vzorca"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extend Pattern"
msgstr "Razširi vzorec"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extend the pattern top, left, right and bottom"
msgstr "Razširi vzorec zgoraj, levo, desno in spodaj"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Center Pattern"
msgstr "Sredinski vzorec"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Center the pattern in the canvas"
msgstr "Centrirajte vzorec na platnu"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crop Canvas To Pattern"
msgstr "Obreži platno na vzorec"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crop the canvas to the extents of the pattern"
msgstr "Obreže platno na obseg vzorca"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crop Canvas To Selection"
msgstr "Obreži platno na izbor"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crop the canvas to the extents of the current selection"
msgstr "Obreže platno do obsega trenutne izbire"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Rows"
msgstr "Vstavi vrstice"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a number of rows represented by a selection area"
msgstr "Vstavi več vrstic, ki jih predstavlja izbirno območje"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert Columns"
msgstr "Vstavi stolpce"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a number of columns represented by a selection area"
msgstr "Vstavi več stolpcev, ki jih predstavlja izbirno območje"

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; Settings menu entries described in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\"> Settings Menu</ulink> "
"chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals &kxstitch; has these application specific "
"menu entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; vnosa menija z nastavitvami so opisani v poglavju "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\"> Meni z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> v &kde; Osnove &kxstitch; ima te menijske vnose za "
"posamezne aplikacije:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format Scales As"
msgstr "Format Lestvice kot"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the scale display format to Stitches, CM or Inches."
msgstr "Spremenite obliko prikaza merila za šive, CM ali palce."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Render Stitches As"
msgstr "Upodabljanje šivov kot"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the way stitches are displayed."
msgstr "Spremenite način prikaza šivov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Render Backstitches As"
msgstr "Upodobi hrbtne šive kot"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the way backstitches are displayed."
msgstr "Spremenite način prikaza hrbtnih šivov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Render Knots As"
msgstr "Upodobi vozle kot"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the way knots are displayed."
msgstr "Spremeni način prikaza vozlov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Highlight"
msgstr "Barvni poudarek"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable or disable color highlight mode"
msgstr "Omogoči ali onemogoči način osvetlitve barv"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Stitches"
msgstr "Prikaži šive"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the stitches"
msgstr "Prikaži ali skrij šive"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Backstitches"
msgstr "Prikaži hrbtne šive"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the backstitches"
msgstr "Prikaži ali skrij hrbtne šive"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show French Knots"
msgstr "Prikaži francoske vozle"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the french knots"
msgstr "Pokaži ali skrij francoske vozle"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Grid"
msgstr "Pokaži mrežo"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the grid"
msgstr "Pokaži ali skrij mrežo"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Background Images"
msgstr "Prikaži slike ozadja"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide all the background images"
msgstr "Prikaži ali skrij vse slike ozadja"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &kxstitch;"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj &kxstitch;"

#. Tag: action
#: commands.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &kxstitch; <link linkend=\"ConfigurationDialog\">configuration dialog</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Odpri &kxstitch; <link linkend=\"ConfigurationDialog\">pogovorno okno "
"konfiguracije</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: commands.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kxstitch; has the common &kde; Help menu items, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Dodatno &kxstitch; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija Pomoč, za več informacij "
"preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."
